*Djeca* su učila o životinjama. (The children were learning about animals.)

*Djeca* su se igrala u parku. (The children were playing in the park.)

*Djece* je bilo mnogo. (There were many children.)

*Djeci* je bilo hladno. (The children were cold.)

*Djecu* su odveli kući. (They took the children home.)

*Djecom* su se divili. (They admired the children.)